{"tid":1841192,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港醫護唔罷工迫政府封關 依家就一車車送非港人病人俾你地","createTime":"2020-01-25T07:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T08:02:06.000Z","uid":78295,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4ecd2c1d83c95fc17a6df643ce25c96723fd2987","tid":1841192,"uid":78295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:38:01.000Z","msg":"1330 #武漢肺炎 #沙頭角 #入境<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎失控，接連有中國旅客轉往香港求醫。《蘋果》獲悉，周四有一名發燒的中國旅客循沙頭角管制站入境，雖獲檢查站截停，最終仍獲准入境香港，由救護車送院。有入境處人員向《蘋果》稱，處方本有權以「傳染病（Contagious disease）」為由拒絕該病者入境，但最終按衛生署要求以「人道理由」准其往港就醫；前線人員質疑口岸作為防疫第一線，但防護物品不足，「連口罩都就快用曬」。<br />\n<br />\n報導全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200125/546WZOBUMNLYOPVVWBT57Q23S4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200125%2F546WZOBUMNLYOPVVWBT57Q23S4&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FSukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=0e9e5b30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200125%2F546WZOBUMNLYOPVVWBT57Q23S4&h=7942a187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200125/546WZOBUMNLYOPVVWBT57Q23S4</a><br />\n#蘋果"},{"pid":"2171c3073fd7df94fd58e6f3b8cd0e4e3c48422e","tid":1841192,"uid":78295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:38:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LiVABPe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLiVABPe.jpg&h=03020345&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4198fdf76b99e63155759e486fffcee4b28bb3c7","tid":1841192,"uid":78295,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:42:35.000Z","msg":"你罷工 可能無左份工 養家重擔壓力大左<br />\n但你同你家人唔會因爲大量中國人衝關而高危染病<br />\n然後陷家產<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔罷 咪全香港一齊死lo"},{"pid":"0f66601ff5efd1cf5457e3ce88a0b6d22398168f","tid":1841192,"uid":78295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ecd2c1d83c95fc17a6df643ce25c96723fd2987","tid":1841192,"uid":78295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:38:01.000Z","msg":"1330 #武漢肺炎 #沙頭角 #入境<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎失控，接連有中國旅客轉往香港求醫。《蘋果》獲悉，周四有一名發燒的中國旅客循沙頭角管制站入境，雖獲檢查站截停，最終仍獲准入境香港，由救護車送院。有入境處人員向《蘋果》稱，處方本有權以「傳染病（Contagious disease）」為由拒絕該病者入境，但最終按衛生署要求以「人道理由」准其往港就醫；前線人員質疑口岸作為防疫第一線，但防護物品不足，「連口罩都就快用曬」。<br />\n<br />\n報導全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200125/546WZOBUMNLYOPVVWBT57Q23S4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200125%2F546WZOBUMNLYOPVVWBT57Q23S4&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FSukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=0e9e5b30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200125%2F546WZOBUMNLYOPVVWBT57Q23S4&h=7942a187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200125/546WZOBUMNLYOPVVWBT57Q23S4</a><br />\n#蘋果"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:53:55.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】稱封關屬「極端措施」 陳健波：大家一家人，唔可以隨便話停<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2RLrMkR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2RLrMkR&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FSukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=acc3646c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2RLrMkR</a>"},{"pid":"57a7a8bc6179ebed9c480daa0fd3a52508d4e375","tid":1841192,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:55:18.000Z","msg":"唔好再-0-0<br />\n<br />\n唔好當為左香港 你當為左自己條命<br />\n唔值得救藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b8d76568c12247dd3ffd26ce869bcd233f56d28","tid":1841192,"uid":78295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57a7a8bc6179ebed9c480daa0fd3a52508d4e375","tid":1841192,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:55:18.000Z","msg":"唔好再-0-0<br />\n<br />\n唔好當為左香港 你當為左自己條命<br />\n唔值得救藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:58:24.000Z","msg":"唔好成日拉埋香港藍絲黎spin走因為非港人衝關ge罷工最大原因<img src=\"/assets/f